added.title: The Wheel of Vomit
added.description: Chef finally gets to show off his fancy culinary skills in an eating challenge where each dish is a tastebud's nightmare. The last camper still eating wins immunity. The rest are all up for elimination.

added.title: Paddle Field Earth
added.description: Today's challenge involves canoeing, hiking and mountain climbing. It's just like normal summer camp!! Except that you canoe over a waterfall, hike through a geyser field and climb a mountain that's actually the world's biggest beehive. It's nothing like summer camp.

added.title: The Truth, The Pole Truth and Nothing But the Truth
added.description: If spending the day balancing on a pole under the direct sun with no food in your tummy sounds like a fun time you are going to love today's challenge.

added.title: Tortoise Rigamortis
added.description: With just 5 campers remaining things are getting tense. So today is just about having fun taking selfies with wild animals. Everyone had their rabies shot?

added.title: Caved by the Bell
added.description: The final 4 get must wander through a dark and spooky cave hunting for coins. The challenge only gets worse when they discover that something is also hunting them.

added.title: Braces
added.description: When the Bears go to the dentist, Panda gets braces. But, Panda finds out his braces grant him super abilities and the power goes to his head.

added.title: Christmas Movies
added.description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

added.title: Imaginary Friend
added.description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

added.title: The Mall
added.description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

added.title: Tunnels
added.description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

added.title: The Prince and the Dark Lord of Moletown
added.description: Prince Ivandoe is unsurprised to discover that he is worshipped by a group of moles. Their leader, the sinister Dark Lord of Moletown, is convinced that Ivandoe's magic potion once bestowed upon him the ability to see in the daylight. The Dark Lord now wishes for Ivandoe to use his magic on his moley minions, so that they might rise up as an unstoppable army and take over the forest! When the moles realize Ivandoe isn't actually magic, things go a little "squiggly".
added.seriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe
added.originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

added.title: The Prince and the Squire-Off
added.description: Bert enters a prestigious Squire-Off tournament in order to prove himself worthy of being Prince Ivandoe's squire. His competitors are Toby (Prince Svan's squire); Maggie (Jezabel's squire); Gnaomi (a thinly disguised Sassy Gnome) and … Ducky! Bert's devotion to Prince Ivandoe eventually wins him the coveted Golden Grooming Brush. Unfortunately for Ivandoe, it also wins Bert his freedom…
added.seriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe
added.originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

added.title: The Prince and the Kissy Curse
added.description: An arrogant little frogman needs the help of Prince Ivandoe to lift his curse and become the big, beautiful bullfrog he once was. Due to a technical error, Prince Ivandoe's arms have been magically replaced by slimy froggy ones. So he has no choice but to help lift the curse in order to restore his princely arms. The Frogman's hopeless attempts to find a True Love's kiss end in failure. So Ivandoe and Bert convince him that his only hope is to earn the forgiveness of The Batwitch - his ex-girlfriend - who was responsible for cursing him in the first place.
added.seriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe
added.originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

added.title: Pajamas Party
added.description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

added.title: The Soundhouse
added.description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

added.title: Puff Paint
added.description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

added.title: Susie Appreciation Day
added.description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

added.title: Campers Above the Bed
added.description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

removed.title: Hot Sauce
removed.description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

removed.title: Best Bears
removed.description: The Bears must complete their Best-Man duties on the day of Darrell's wedding.

removed.title: Family Troubles
removed.description: Baby Grizz lives on the set of a sitcom in which he stars. But when a cooler kid joins the cast, Grizz feels threatened.

removed.title: Mom App
removed.description: Hoping to finally get the mom-experience, the Bears use an app that'll bring a mom right to their door.

removed.title: Crowbar Jones: Origins
removed.description: Grizz pitches his Crowbar Jones prequel film to Nom Nom, hoping Nom Nom will agree to appear in the movie.

removed.title: Circling The Drain
removed.description: Julia gets between Caleb and Priya during the most painful memory game of all time.

removed.title: Breaking Up Is Hard To Do
removed.description: Caleb is desperate to put his relationship with Priya back together while the campers tear apart the largest objects they can find.

removed.title: Haulin' n' Ballin'
removed.description: The fate of Priya and Caleb's relationship hangs in the balance as Zee struggles to keep a secret. And it all plays out during a brutal game of human pinball.

removed.title: Fun Fight at the Oh Cake Corral
removed.description: It's definitely no cake walk as Campers compete in the ultimate island bake-off. A very special guest judge even stops by for a bite!

removed.title: Canoe Believe It?
removed.description: During a fun-filled day of canoe jousting, a special friendship is founded and an outed cheater gets pounded.
